<h2>About Print Anything</h2>
<p>
This utility provides the ability to produce a customised printable view of any data in Salesforce.com. Examples are Quotes, Contracts, Order forms, Thank You letters, SLA's etc.
</p><p>Used in conjuction with a PDF print driver, these views may be saved in Acrobat format. Alternatively, using a service such as eFax, they may be faxed directly to a customer.
</p><p>A printable view is created using a print "package" which contains all of the config, template and styles required to query the correct data and display in a specific way. Creation of packages is a somewhat technical process since it requires creation of SOQL queries, HTML templates and CSS but no actual programming is required. All execution of the result is driven through a single s-control invoked by a custom link or button on the record detail page.
</p>
<p>Here is an example. A quote from the
<a target="quote" href="http://www.salesforce.com/appexchange/detail_overview.jsp?id=a0330000000ilckAAA">Sales Quote with Product Line Items</a>
application, rendered using Print Anything...</p>
